text: Daniel Estrada (born 27 February 1990) is a Chilean long distance runner who specialises in the marathon. He competed in the men's marathon event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male long-distance runners Category:Chilean male marathon runners Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Chile
